QUEST SYSTEM

Quests are tasks given by NPCs in the game world.  Completing quests
rewards you with experience points, credits, and sometimes special items
or faction reputation.

COMMANDS
  quests                lists your active quests and progress
  quests completed      lists quests you have finished
  quests <id>           shows details on a specific quest

HOW TO GET QUESTS
  Talk to NPCs.  Many NPCs will offer quests if you say certain keywords
  to them.  For example:
    say work         (many quest givers respond to this)
    say job
    say quest

  Not all NPCs offer quests.  Explore and experiment.

COMPLETING QUESTS
  Quest objectives are tracked automatically.  When you complete an
  objective (pick up an item, reach a location, talk to someone), the
  system updates your progress.  When all objectives are met, the quest
  completes and you receive your reward.

STARTING QUESTS IN PRAXIS
  Marta (general store)  - lost caravan supplies
  Griz (weapons shop)    - find a CS deserter
  Rocky (bar)            - track a Cyber-Knight's trail

